Hot Air Balloons
-----------------
This mod adds craftable and ridable hot air balloons.

Controls:
    right click with fuel(like coal) item: increase heat and buoyancy (*)
    right click without fuel (coal is a fuel): enter or leave balloon
    left, right, up, down (default WASD): accelerate the balloon
    sneak (default shift): decrease heat, lowering buoyancy
    jump (default space): turn the balloon towards where the player is looking